 		`DSPL_ERROR_SIZE` 	Argument vector size is wrong (`n < 1`). <BR>	
		`DSPL_ERROR_POLY_ORD` Polynomial order less than 0. <BR>
		
	\author
		Sergey Bakhurin. 
		www.dsplib.org	                                                               

*/



